AdditionalAnnotation.DefaultContentUri This specifies the default ContentUri.
AdditionalAnnotation.DefaultSortOrder Be used query method, if you do not specify how to sort.
AdditionalAnnotation.ProjectionMap If you want to replace the column name, then you use the ProjectionMap annotation.
